{"id":28035,"date":"2019-04-22T11:01:01","date_gmt":"2019-04-22T07:01:01","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=28035"},"modified":"2021-11-17T12:05:25","modified_gmt":"2021-11-17T08:05:25","slug":"people-questioned-grave","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/04\/22\/people-questioned-grave\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Akhirah: People are tested and questioned in the grave"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Asma&#8217; bint Abi Bakr reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>It has been revealed to me that you will be put to trial in the grave, similar to the trial of the False Messiah. As for the believer or Muslim, he will say: Muhammad came to us with clear evidence and we answered him and believed in him. It will be said: Sleep in peace, for we knew you had conviction. As for the hypocrite or the doubter, he will say: I do not know, for I heard people saying something and I repeated it.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7287<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Bukhari<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0633\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0621\u064e \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0628\u064e\u0643\u0652\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u062a\u0652 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e <strong>\u0623\u064f\u0648\u062d\u0650\u064a\u064e \u0625\u0650\u0644\u064e\u0649\u0651\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0643\u064f\u0645\u0652 \u062a\u064f\u0641\u0652\u062a\u064e\u0646\u064f\u0648\u0646